  Cheng-sin5 piN7-lang5 chin chu3-sin5 teh sia2 phoe. Pat8-e5 piN7-lang5 houN3-ki5 ka7 mng7: “Li2 teh chhong3 siaN2 ?” 
  “Mai3 kiau2-jiau2 goa2, goa2 teh sia2 chit8-tiuN chin tiong7-iau3 e5 phoe.” 
  “Sia2 hou7 siaN2-lang5 ?” 
  “Tong-jian5 si7 sia2 hou7 goa2 ka-ti7 ah.” 
  “Tau3-te2 si7 sia2 siaN2 ?” 
  “Goa2 na2 e7 chai ? Phoe bin5-a2-chai3 chiah e7 siu--tioh8 ah.” 
  Chit8-e5 a2-tah a2-tah e5 lang5 che7 ke3-theng5-chhia. Kau3-ui7 e5 si5, su-ki kong2: “75 khou.” 
