  Keng-koe3 tng5-ki5 e5 ti7-liau5, cheng-sin5-kho e5 i-seng mng7 cha-bou2 piN7-lang5: “Li2 chit-ma2 kam2 iau2 e7 siuN7 kong2 li2 si7 ChiuN2 hu-jin5 ?” 
  “Oh! Boe7 ah lah.” 
  “Ho2, an2-ni li2 e7-sai3 chhut-iN7 ah.” 
  “To-sia7, chhiaN2 li2 chiong siau3-toaN kia3 hou7 ChiuN2 chong2-thong2.” 
  “Oe2! Li2 toa3 chhiu7-a2-teng2 chhong3-siaN2 ? Kin2 loh8-lai5 ah! Beh tan5 lui5 ah neh!” 
  “To7-si7 an2-ni goa2 m7 chiah peh khi2-lai5 chhiu7-a2-teng2. Lian5 saN-hoe3 gin2-a2 ma7 chai-iaN2 tan5-lui5-kong e5 si5 boe7-sai2 khia7 toa3 chhiu7-a2-kha.”
  “Lin2 sio-ti7 si7 an2-choaN2 ? Phoa3-piN7 hiouh ?” 
  “Koh khah giam5-tiong7.” 
  “Si2--khi3 hiouh ?” 
  “Koh khah giam5-tiong7. Si7 thau5-khak phaiN2--khi3.” 
  “Kam2 e7 an2-ni ? I tu2 chiah chiong khiam3--goa2 e5 chiN5 heng5 liau2 nia7 neh.” 
  “Sou2-i2 m7 chiah kong2 i thau5-khak phaiN2--khi3 ah.” 
  Chit8-e5 bong7-siong2 ka-ti7 si7 niau2-chhi2 e5 cheng-sin5 piN7-lang5, keng-koe3 ku2-ni5 e5 ti7-liau5, i2-keng e7-sai2 chhut-iN7. I-seng sang3 i kau3 piN7-iN7 mng5-khau2. PiN7-lang5 hui-siong5 kin2-tiuN mng7 i-seng: 
  “Goa2 chin-chiaN3 e7-sai2 chhut-iN7 ah hiouh ?” 
  “Si7 an2-choaN2 leh ?” 
  “Li2 khoaN3, mng5-khau2 u7 chit8-chiah niau.” 
  “Li2 i2-keng m7-si7 niau-chhi2 ah. Teh kiaN siaN2 ?” 
  “Goa2 chai-iaN2 goa2 m7-si7 niau-chhi2 lah. Tan7-si7, niau-a2 kam2 chai ?” 
  Cheng-sin5 piN7-lang5 chhiu2 giah8 tio3-koaN ti7 ek8-ti5 teh tio3-hi5, i-seng kiaN5--koe3-lai5, eng7 un-jiu5 e5 siaN mng7 i: “kin-a2-jit8 tio3 boe7-chio2 houhN ?” 
  Penn7-lang5 in3-kong2: “Cheng-sin5-penn7! Ek8-ti5 nah u7 hi5 thang tio3!”
  U7 chit8-e5 lang5 chhiam Ta2-chia-lo2, chhiam it-liok8 (16), ko2-jian5 hou7 i chhiam--tioh8. 
  Peng5-iu2 mng7 i: “Li2 na2 e7 chai-iaN2 si7 16, si7 tui3 to2-ui7 theh8--lai5 e5 beng5-pai5 ?”
  I in3 kong2: “Goa2 cho3-bang7 bang7--tioh8-e5. Goa2 bang7-kiN3 chit8-chiah kau2-a2 teh peh chhiu7-a2, sou2-i2 si7 kau2 (9) peh (8). 9 ka 8 soah m7-si7 16 ?” 
  (Hong-hiong3 Te7 18 ki5, 1992 ni5 9 goeh8) 
